Strings based practice questions

1) Write a program to input user's first name and print its length
    Program:- 
    name = input("Enter your name: ")
    print("length of your name is: ",len(name))
    Output:- 
    Enter your name: varshini
    length of your name is: 8
    
2) Write a program to find the occurence of '$' in a string 
    Program:-
    str = "Hello$ $World$"
    print(str.count("$"))
    Output:- 
    3
